native.query: SELECT repo.id AS "repoId", repo.origin as "repoOrigin", repo.name as "repoName", repo."fullName" as "repoFullName", repo.private as "repoVisibility", "mainBranch", org.id AS "orgId", org.name AS "orgName" FROM "vcs_Repository" As repo JOIN "vcs_Organization" AS org ON org.id=repo.organization
